data.description: Wonderful Assemblage of 50 +/- Acres in prime location, only blocks from Trilith Studios. Imagine the possibilities of what can be done with this land. Land is being sold simultaneously with 539 Veteran Parkway and 551 Veterans Parkway. Currently zoned residential. This exceptional land is located in close proximity to a bustling commercial district. Within a short walk, you will find an array of shops, theatres, restaurants, hotels, and amenities that cater to the needs of residents and visitors alike. The presence of these commercial establishments adds convenience and accessibility to the area, making it an ideal location for various purposes. The excitement of all of the movies and TV shows being made within walking distance.
